> I figured a breach wasn't all that bad at that point, and I really wanted to get some attackers set up, to not be on the back foot forever.
@FlakManiak 
that's the wrong way to think about it grenade mech only  gives 1 permanent attack so it's not a good long term investment. Grenade mech derives its value from opponents inability to defend or forcing out inefficent defence. So when opponent rushes you with Gmechs your objective should be to make sure you can defend efficently.Allowing a breach is the opposite of that

